# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Arkiv Sync — environment. Copy this file to `.env` and fill PRIVATE_KEY.
# `.env` is gitignored. NEVER commit it. NEVER paste a key holding real funds.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# REQUIRED for writing to Arkiv.
# A THROWAWAY testnet wallet, funded with GLM on the Braga faucet:
#   https://braga.hoodi.arkiv.network/faucet/
# This key signs Arkiv writes LOCALLY (viem). It never leaves your machine and is
# never logged. Use a disposable burner — Arkiv Sync refuses non-testnet chains.
PRIVATE_KEY=0xYOUR_THROWAWAY_TESTNET_PRIVATE_KEY

# ─── Optional overrides (sensible defaults are pre-set + verified) ───

# Your own Sepolia RPC URL (e.g. Alchemy/Infura). If unset, a pool of public
# RPCs with automatic rotation/fallback is used — no signup required.
# SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=

# Override the Arkiv (Braga) RPC. Default is the verified Braga endpoint.
# ARKIV_RPC_URL=https://braga.hoodi.arkiv.network/rpc
